{"tid":1897850,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國共和黨: 香港抗爭者要懂得靈活變通, be water","createTime":"2020-02-26T03:05:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T13:59:08.000Z","uid":134071,"like":115,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"d2c95985390e664c8e28d65d9ea9c9b61b8032f3","tid":1897850,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:05:00.000Z","msg":"美國共和黨Solomon Yue<br />\n<br />\n- 香港抗爭者一定要懂得靈活變通, be water<br />\n- 2020未必可取消功能組別選舉. &nbsp;即使如此, 大家不能放棄選舉.<br />\n- <strong>在2020年立法會選舉取得過半數後, 可在立法會提交「雙普選方案」</strong><br />\n- <strong>中聯辦主任駱惠寧講過 如果泛民係2020年立法會選舉大勝, 等同代表香港人拒絕中共管治.</strong><br />\n- 所以, 不能放棄勝出2020年立法會選舉的機會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/4H1kAJ6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4H1kAJ6.jpg&h=0b6ddd5e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1232491199040122883\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1232491199040122883&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWGWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=909dcd80\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1232491199040122883&h=20d847fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1232491199040122883</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1232493501348114432\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1232493501348114432&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWGWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=cd609f7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1232493501348114432&h=e8e91d01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1232493501348114432</a>"},{"pid":"3878b5646a1579429057cb40a9c87ce4d3728a7b","tid":1897850,"uid":134071,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:05:09.000Z","msg":"專訪Solomon Yue: 我是跟美國副總統Pence合作協助「香港人」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1833743/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1833743/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/9GeGs8D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9GeGs8D.jpg&h=743a2be8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fce4813b18a5bcd55b7560a41d072a9acb662ef8","tid":1897850,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:05:44.000Z","msg":"be water<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d51a86a605bee78613001dab7f02f96ecad502df","tid":1897850,"uid":101906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:06:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d829c003e5c4454234e2a7c62b58d12559fdce5","tid":1897850,"uid":146030,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:06:20.000Z","msg":"佢連香港政制都唔識"},{"pid":"519c9efdb3c8fde1411470a3eb1590d27dd32812","tid":1897850,"uid":205482,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:06:26.000Z","msg":"推 also be humble<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n立場facebook留言：廢除功能組別 投白票都唔投泛民 連登係鬼 泛民賣手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1897800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1897800</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"eb6bad5b2c74d3462d79d40cad5a968d83dc7c7d","tid":1897850,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:07:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59adabcece184d9735047588137bcdd51c4abed9","tid":1897850,"uid":104767,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:08:17.000Z","msg":"幾日前我本身係寫：<br />\n<br />\n我覺得要攻立會過半可以，前提係<br />\n1. 全世界知道制度不公<br />\n2. 選舉不能耗費其他抗爭資源，應避免成為抗爭焦點<br />\n<br />\n如果候選代議士有類似梁天琦嘅革命思想，有全面推翻現有制度嘅覺梧，我會比宜家更支持全力攻立法會，甚至功能組別。其實好多人點解盲反制度內抗爭，係因為代議士一次又一次令大眾失望。非不信任代議士動機，而係不信任其能力。<br />\n<br />\n如果政黨中人可以進步成體制內革命家，而非繼續做敵進一步、我守一步嘅抵抗者，問題就易解決。<br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月真係泛民重拾大眾信心嘅最後機會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係一鬧泛民就俾人屈毛<br />\n想泛民本土化換嚟嘅係冷嘲熱諷，話我哋係少數一定要妥協<br />\n求仁得仁<br />\n而家我一撚定唔會投泛民兼做白票撚<br />\n屈毛屈得咁開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad698c35b5a0c78acabe560bb49ae13961bb019","tid":1897850,"uid":64953,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:08:34.000Z","msg":"所羅門唔係大台<br />\n但其實勇武同投票係冇抵觸<br />\n大家各有各做咪得"},{"pid":"6e1b1e22b38ef627dc5b31c86c6c2c2a2a799be0","tid":1897850,"uid":112583,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:10:03.000Z","msg":"一步步黎, 立法會贏埋<br />\n再推雙普選方案<br />\n拎埋政府資源 打壓港共<br />\n<br />\n贏唔贏唔知<br />\n咁樣行一定唔會輸"},{"pid":"9451801a540ad28942e6108ece23965f994695dd","tid":1897850,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:10:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18c94ef80a62dbff6b8d44d4f726c28267682f30","tid":1897850,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59adabcece184d9735047588137bcdd51c4abed9","tid":1897850,"uid":104767,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:08:17.000Z","msg":"幾日前我本身係寫：<br />\n<br />\n我覺得要攻立會過半可以，前提係<br />\n1. 全世界知道制度不公<br />\n2. 選舉不能耗費其他抗爭資源，應避免成為抗爭焦點<br />\n<br />\n如果候選代議士有類似梁天琦嘅革命思想，有全面推翻現有制度嘅覺梧，我會比宜家更支持全力攻立法會，甚至功能組別。其實好多人點解盲反制度內抗爭，係因為代議士一次又一次令大眾失望。非不信任代議士動機，而係不信任其能力。<br />\n<br />\n如果政黨中人可以進步成體制內革命家，而非繼續做敵進一步、我守一步嘅抵抗者，問題就易解決。<br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月真係泛民重拾大眾信心嘅最後機會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係一鬧泛民就俾人屈毛<br />\n想泛民本土化換嚟嘅係冷嘲熱諷，話我哋係少數一定要妥協<br />\n求仁得仁<br />\n而家我一撚定唔會投泛民兼做白票撚<br />\n屈毛屈得咁開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:11:53.000Z","msg":"唔好灰心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"779cb07d46b139b296f01453698e51dc10a47f14","tid":1897850,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ad698c35b5a0c78acabe560bb49ae13961bb019","tid":1897850,"uid":64953,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:08:34.000Z","msg":"所羅門唔係大台<br />\n但其實勇武同投票係冇抵觸<br />\n大家各有各做咪得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:12:48.000Z","msg":"所羅門都話過自己唔係大台, 係伙伴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2a35e8fa65ac1e6f3f33fc30947036ea8b5bc5c","tid":1897850,"uid":161711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:13:28.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"57cad47b7958b02c957413dc83f29627d406959d","tid":1897850,"uid":51620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:13:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a6a7e7f7250ed6e1438363e14acde47d1abfbf","tid":1897850,"uid":234961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:14:41.000Z","msg":"借ac:是咁的，我係西環駱先生<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1896677\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1896677</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2072f6d619142fe17b822b87f9e23902fa98d33a","tid":1897850,"uid":77180,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:15:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實唔係問題<br />\n但議員/國際team不如過多幾次美國傾傾先<br />\n睇下可唔可以掌握到更穩陣嘅plan<br />\n支持玩選舉嘅好多當左係做場大龍鳯比人睇<br />\n但呢個心態係有問題<br />\n中共唔跟規矩呢樣野本身係有哂歷史<br />\n外國自己都知事實係點<br />\n未必要我地花幾年時間同抗爭機會成本去證明<br />\n所以個重點根本上係外國會唔會有行動</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c80d6065295fae91541d4ec024ac675000bb171e","tid":1897850,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:16:09.000Z","msg":"做狗同支持民主都冇抵觸"},{"pid":"8d503443b4abaad305399226ab235456fca17ae6","tid":1897850,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"779cb07d46b1