求仁得仁<br />\n而家我一撚定唔會投泛民兼做白票撚<br />\n屈毛屈得咁開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T08:30:21.000Z","msg":"本土派最少有4成人支持"},{"pid":"a61c909453944ddc3f50d6c1c4d4860409a029a1","tid":1897850,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T08:30:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a89524f0010a17a895f57d4d88608bdfb3814c","tid":1897850,"uid":119895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T08:43:02.000Z","msg":"大力推呢個post"},{"pid":"9a5fbdedcc9ec28f6b6a7ba859148b47e1622915","tid":1897850,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:02:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ad7f60bbd0559be85ef36880784cfc2e1462d9","tid":1897850,"uid":14399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:57:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ffc7fe82fe6006a60e4591e903b7a4826d0fce56","tid":1897850,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:59:36.000Z","msg":"on9，立法會冇動議權架，條友了解下背景先講野啦，次次都係咁"},{"pid":"2c5a6c697b578d40a4b8bb25916fedfd91213b02","tid":1897850,"uid":286131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T10:00:00.000Z","msg":"0pish"},{"pid":"1f3b8ec4d8c99f59d57c73f0274d77527fabdfbe","tid":1897850,"uid":92811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2d829c003e5c4454234e2a7c62b58d12559fdce5","tid":1897850,"uid":146030,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:06:20.000Z","msg":"佢連香港政制都唔識"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T10:04:20.000Z","msg":"假民主笑民主大國唔識政治<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐華盛頓個班分分鐘比維尼清楚蝗國內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8522f764d73527fd07aaf15567770e9305e7523","tid":1897850,"uid":170143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,